build.md
     1тЖТ# The build command
     3тЖТThe build command is used to render your book:
     4тЖТ
     5тЖТ```bash
     6тЖТmdbook build
     7тЖТ```
     8тЖТ
     9тЖТIt will try to parse your `SUMMARY.md` file to understand the structure of your
    10тЖТbook and fetch the corresponding files. Note that this will also create files
    11тЖТmentioned in `SUMMARY.md` which are not yet present.
    12тЖТ
    13тЖТThe rendered output will maintain the same directory structure as the source for
    14тЖТconvenience. Large books will therefore remain structured when rendered.
    15тЖТ
    16тЖТ#### Specify a directory
    25тЖТ#### `--open`
    30тЖТ#### `--dest-dir`

